nodes.text: Totally 20: The Phantom Menace is a 32-page magazine in honor of Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace released on February 2, 2012 by Titan Magazines. It has features, puzzles and games and ten pages in 3-D. Features include a segment all about Darth Maul and his abilities, Jedi training, the Top 5 movie moments, instructions on how to make a lightsaber and a brand new comic strip called the Duel of the Fates!. The magazine also comes with a C-3PO grabber arm, 3-D glasses and stickers.
